About Country Inn and Suites by Radisson, Sahibabad

Experience unparalleled luxury at this opulent property known for its pure veg dining options, well-appointed rooms, a lavish spa and world-class amenities.

  • Pamper your body with luxury treatments and wellness therapies at the on-site spa.
  • Take a refreshing dip in the crystal-clear swimming pool.
  • Stick to your workout routine at the state-of-the-art fitness centre.
  • Delight your senses with pure vegetarian Thai, Lebanese, Mexican and Indian delicacies at the on-site restaurants.
